{"tid":745413,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇連登揾客王 漢方藥林個中醫","createTime":"2018-07-16T17:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T01:15:20.000Z","uid":149949,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a3cc5cd98f51001873a8fd45a39e18672e9887","tid":745413,"uid":149949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/012755_d1280a17aea7a13063933bd9b6340085.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F012755_d1280a17aea7a13063933bd9b6340085.png&h=b2c01f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個醫師成日話其他中醫廢，自己就運用經方好勁。我就抱着一試嘅態度上去，點知遇到個沉醉於自己世界嘅人，診所綠色裝修，拍烏蠅。唔講咁多，總結就是：講就天下無敵，食完啲藥症狀差咗，食咗三日一啲效都冇，唔會複診了，因為之前睇大隻醫生仲好，起碼佢肯同我溝通，提醒我多啲日常生活要注意的是，食完佢2天藥我症狀就改善。<br />\n有冇巴打絲打都去咗睇？大家一齊分享下。同埋係連登拉客係咪觸犯條例？因為好似醫生唔可以到處拉客？"},{"pid":"24ddef7a650610f31a98a8b03899f48d8b2e0874","tid":745413,"uid":149949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0a3cc5cd98f51001873a8fd45a39e18672e9887","tid":745413,"uid":149949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/012755_d1280a17aea7a13063933bd9b6340085.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F012755_d1280a17aea7a13063933bd9b6340085.png&h=b2c01f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個醫師成日話其他中醫廢，自己就運用經方好勁。我就抱着一試嘅態度上去，點知遇到個沉醉於自己世界嘅人，診所綠色裝修，拍烏蠅。唔講咁多，總結就是：講就天下無敵，食完啲藥症狀差咗，食咗三日一啲效都冇，唔會複診了，因為之前睇大隻醫生仲好，起碼佢肯同我溝通，提醒我多啲日常生活要注意的是，食完佢2天藥我症狀就改善。<br />\n有冇巴打絲打都去咗睇？大家一齊分享下。同埋係連登拉客係咪觸犯條例？因為好似醫生唔可以到處拉客？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"學佢push"},{"pid":"2a977f54b23201d70cec0765398ce2eb6638bcdb","tid":745413,"uid":126178,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:55:09.000Z","msg":"我係個到睇 唔覺得無生意<br />\n都有啲一睇就知唔係連登R返黎既客仔（嬸嬸）<br />\n上次等左成個鐘 次次5-6點都要等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇左咁耐 覺得呢個醫師睇得幾好<br />\n可能每人感覺唔同"},{"pid":"5397d6dabaf5f4ec141fedd6a61cc7bca786e367","tid":745413,"uid":126178,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/140049_44d441e54948a256a6c90c7d07f85efd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F140049_44d441e54948a256a6c90c7d07f85efd.png&h=c9eba120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩先去睇完 唔好話我收錢打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4677b5a58422a8064733caf5b958c3943fca46ae","tid":745413,"uid":149949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"我上次去唔使等，都係五六點，只係得我一個人。真係好彩"},{"pid":"99dc5b7786c6e5f3129595b173cdfada73be14e2","tid":745413,"uid":190101,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"我睇過，個日六點去到得我一條友<br />\n<br />\n食完藥都係無用....."},{"pid":"7aa4779ace5221826921c4494cdf0bf751fcc99e","tid":745413,"uid":149949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5397d6dabaf5f4ec141fedd6a61cc7bca786e367","tid":745413,"uid":126178,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/140049_44d441e54948a256a6c90c7d07f85efd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F140049_44d441e54948a256a6c90c7d07f85efd.png&h=c9eba120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩先去睇完 唔好話我收錢打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"你睇左幾耐啦？係咩事睇？"},{"pid":"f83ee3dcf28797fab4e0e5b860d76e4f6b0cd5ab","tid":745413,"uid":56141,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:24:07.000Z","msg":"睇左三星期濕